            To publish a new release:
            1. Build, sign, notarize, staple the app
            2. Create zip: ditto -c -k - -keepParent Lenny.app Lenny-vX.Y.zip
            3. Sign for Sparkle: sign_update Lenny-vX.Y.zip
            4. Add a new <item> below with the edSignature and length
            5. Upload zip to GitHub Releases
            6. Commit appcast.xml and push
        -->
